      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I've babied it since day one and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
